nd excitement. This not only contributes to a happy life but also helps them remain healthy. Secondly, older people spend half their lives working and earning a lot of money, so they should spend money to fulfill their desires and dreams after retirement. As a result, in their later stages of life, they may enjoy and feel relaxed after doing a lot of work.<br><br>However, despite these advantages, this situation can be considered largely disadvantageous. Of particular concern is the fact that if parents cannot save any materialistic things or capital, then children can become disappointed. This is because it is a guardian's significant responsibility to save money and things for their children. However, if parents do not leave these things for their upcoming generation, it can negatively impact their relationships. In addition, there are many situations where people suffer from bankruptcy. At that time, they hope their elder parents can save them with their retirement savings. But if the elder people do not save money, they cannot help them in this problem. Mostly, older people save their money for the future.<br><br>In conclusion, although older people have the freedom to enjoy their life by spending their money on themselves, they cannot ignore their responsibility towards their children's future.</div></div> <div class="flex flex-row items-center mt-9 essay-Type s-eFLaT0Qt8AF8"><img src="/img/score.svg" class="w-6 h-6 my-1 mr-2 imgshadowed s-eFLaT0Qt8AF8" alt="Icon"> <p class="text-base font-bold s-eFLaT0Qt8AF8" data-svelte-h="svelte-yh6cgo">Estimated Band Score(s)</p></div> <h1 class="mx-5 mt-1 text-xs font-normal text-center text-black my-web-font s-eFLaT0Qt8AF8" data-svelte-h="svelte-z3eonx">Based on your performance in terms of task coverage, grammatical accuracy and lexical appropriateness, here is an estimation of your score.</h1> <div class="mt-2 border-2 rounded border-neutral-800 overflow-clip bg-[#F8F0E3]  s-eFLaT0Qt8AF8"><div class="flex flex-row px-2 